  "text": "Fine-tuned the node positioning in the sprite generator. The nodes (circular elements on sides of the body) were overlapping too much with the body rectangle. Changed the positioning from `STROKE/2` to `STROKE` distance from body edge, so now only the stroke width overlaps rather than part of the filled area. This gives a cleaner look where nodes appear properly attached to the body rather than embedded in it.",
